---
import Button from '../common/Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-cream" aria-labelledby="philosophy-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase text-forest-500 mb-3 block">
        Philosophy
      </span>
      <h2 id="philosophy-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-forest-900 mb-8">
        Where Classical Ayurveda Meets Modern Science
      </h2>

      <div class="relative bg-gold-100/50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gold-500/20">
        <span class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-5xl" aria-hidden="true">🌿</span>

        <p class="text-earth-800/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Ayurveda is not alternative medicine — it is original medicine. With roots stretching back
          thousands of years, it offers a complete system of understanding the body, mind, and their
          connection to nature.
        </p>
        <p class="text-earth-800/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          But ancient wisdom alone is not enough. Dr. Pradnya believes in validating classical protocols
          through modern research — combining the depth of Ayurvedic diagnosis with the precision of
          contemporary clinical science.
        </p>
        <p class="text-earth-800/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The result is a healing approach that respects tradition while embracing evidence — practical,
          personalized, and effective for modern lifestyles.
        </p>

        <Button href="/contact" variant="primary">
          Start Your Healing Journey
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
